Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.40,0:06:11.70,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(145,411)}惣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.24,0:06:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}不知不覺間我又坐上了{\rED} EVA
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.05,0:06:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}又被放了上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.45,0:06:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}反正這個廢物也不會動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.52,0:06:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}不…廢物應該是我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.00,0:06:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}沒人需要我這種人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.63,0:06:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}我這種人已經沒人要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.01,0:06:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}沒有人需要無法駕駛{\rED} EVA {\r}的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.87,0:06:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}你在別人心中追尋自己呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.50,0:06:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}少囉嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.23,0:06:45.07,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【害怕分離】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.92,0:06:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}你害怕獨自一個人對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.69,0:06:48.36,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【害怕分離】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.01,0:06:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}你是因為自己也會和別人一起消失才害怕的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.36,0:06:52.86,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【害怕分離】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.35,0:06:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}所以才駕駛{\rED} EVA
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.24,0:06:55.74,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【固著】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.03,0:06:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}少囉嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.62,0:06:57.37,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【固著】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.97,0:06:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}少囉嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.78,0:06:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,550)\fs32}少囉嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.05,0:07:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,550)}我才不想被你這種人偶說教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.00,0:07:03.04,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【第{\rED} 3 {\r}個角色】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.08,0:07:04.63,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【綾波零，她的情況】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.46,0:07:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}我是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.90,0:07:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}綾波零
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.56,0:07:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}你是…誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.13,0:07:11.59,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【綾波零】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.18,0:07:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}你也是綾波零
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.30,0:07:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}對，被稱為綾波零的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.83,0:07:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}大家都是被稱為綾波零的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.23,0:07:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}為什麼每個都是我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.83,0:07:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}因為別人都叫我們綾波零啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.11,0:07:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}你為什麼擁有虛假的心和身體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.40,0:07:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}不是虛假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.02,0:07:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}因為我就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.15,0:07:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.90,0:07:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}你是一個叫{\rED}碇{\r}源堂的人類利用虛假的靈魂製造出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.50,0:07:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}你不過是像人類那樣行事的虛假物體而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.22,0:07:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}你看，你身體裡有個黑暗、什麼都看不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.36,0:07:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}什麼也不懂的心對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.33,0:07:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}真正的你就在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.17,0:07:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}我就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.12,0:08:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}我是由過往的時間，及跟他人的關聯所造就的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.43,0:08:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}與他人的接觸形成了現在的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.34,0:08:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}人的接觸和時間的流逝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.05,0:08:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}會漸漸改變我的心的形態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.24,0:08:17.45,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【那就是羈絆？】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.80,0:08:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.03,0:08:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}它造就了至今為止被叫做綾波零的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.68,0:08:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}它也將造就今後的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.50,0:08:26.79,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【那就是羈絆？】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.40,0:08:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}但是真正的你不止一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.23,0:08:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}只是，你不知道而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.30,0:08:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}因為不想看到，所以不自覺的逃避而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.76,0:08:38.85,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【因為害怕】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.20,0:08:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}因為自己或許不是人的模樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.92,0:08:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}迄今為止的我也可能會消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.48,0:08:47.60,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【所以害怕】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.02,0:08:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}害怕自己會消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.25,0:08:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}害怕自己會從大家的心中消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.15,0:08:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.52,0:08:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}我不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.89,0:09:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}只屬於自己的世界也會消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.45,0:09:01.54,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【害怕吧？】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.96,0:09:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}自己會消失喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.50,0:09:04.54,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【害怕吧？】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.13,0:09:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}不，我很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.90,0:09:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}因為我想死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.95,0:09:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}我想要的是絕望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.80,0:09:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}我想回到虛無
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.47,0:09:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}可是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.96,0:09:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}我無法回到虛無
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.80,0:09:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}那個人不讓我回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.48,0:09:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}還不願讓我回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.98,0:09:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}因為那個人需要，我才存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.81,0:09:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}不過結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.47,0:09:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}不再需要我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.64,0:09:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}被他拋棄了，我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.92,0:09:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}我明明一直祈禱這一天……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.44,0:09:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}但，現在卻很害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.74,0:09:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}來，走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.74,0:09:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}妳就是為了今天，為了這一天而存在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.70,0:09:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}零
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.95,0:09:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.42,0:09:51.46,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【然後——】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.54,0:09:53.42,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【人類的補完開始了】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.80,0:10:00.01,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【再看{\rED}碇{\r}真嗣】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.06,0:10:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}這個感覺是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.84,0:10:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}以前好像也有過一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.31,0:10:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}自己身體的形狀好像漸漸消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.42,0:10:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}好舒服…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.01,0:10:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}好像自己擴充得好大好大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.49,0:10:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,550)}無邊無際
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.96,0:10:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,550)}無邊無際
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.20,0:10:21.78,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【這就是人類補完的起點】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.87,0:10:23.07,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【人類失去的東西】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.12,0:10:24.28,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【曾經喪失的心】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.33,0:10:25.62,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【填補那個心的空白】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.66,0:10:27.62,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【心和靈魂的補完即將開始】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.66,0:10:28.87,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【一切將回歸虛無】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.91,0:10:31.04,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【人類的補完開始了】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.46,0:10:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.39,0:10:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}並不是重歸於虛無
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.32,0:10:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}只不過是讓一切回歸起點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.17,0:10:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}回到這個世界失去已久的母親懷裡而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.83,0:10:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}所有的心將合而為一，得到永遠的安寧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.02,0:10:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}僅此而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.31,0:10:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}那就是補完計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.98,0:10:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.08,0:10:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}我們的心裡永遠都有空白的部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.07,0:10:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}喪失的部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.57,0:10:56.78,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【這就是心靈的飢餓的產生】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.82,0:10:58.40,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【這就是心靈的不安、恐懼的產生】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.20,0:11:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}不管是誰都會害怕心中的黑暗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.76,0:11:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}一生都在試圖逃避、消滅它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.61,0:11:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}可惜只要身為人類就不可能永遠消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.79,0:11:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}因為這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.82,0:11:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}就要把人類的心合而為一讓彼此互相填補
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.74,0:11:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}而且還是由他人來擅自做主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.74,0:11:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}太多管閒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.75,0:11:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}這根本是共謀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.34,0:11:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}不過，你不也是希望這樣的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.43,0:11:23.47,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【Case 1】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.12,0:11:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}這裡是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.80,0:11:27.26,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【葛城美里的情況　（{\rED}Part 1{\r}）】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.05,0:11:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}這是美里心中的我的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.80,0:11:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}就是說，同時也是真嗣心中的我的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.41,0:11:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}我為了找到我自己，必須跟各種各樣的人接觸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.31,0:11:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}必須注視著我的內心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.10,0:11:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}必須注視著我心中的美里小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.69,0:11:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}美里小姐有什麼願望呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.58,0:11:50.75,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【想當好孩子嗎？】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.00,0:11:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}我必須當一個好孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.21,0:11:54.17,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【為什麼？】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.38,0:11:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}爸爸都不在家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.85,0:11:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}所以要幫助媽媽，我必須當好孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.54,0:12:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}可是我不想變成媽媽那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.18,0:12:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}爸爸不在的時候媽媽總是哭泣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.60,0:12:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}我不可以哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.64,0:12:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}不可以撒嬌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.64,0:12:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}所以我一定要做好孩子
