Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.01,0:17:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}我卻可隨時不當她的母親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.04,0:17:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}話是這麼說沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.55,0:17:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}不要啊！媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.70,0:18:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}不要不當我的媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.62,0:18:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}我會做個媽媽喜歡的好孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.36,0:18:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}所以請不要不當我的媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.57,0:18:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,350)\fs32}所以請看著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.60,0:18:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}不要啊媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.82,0:18:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}不要殺我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.29,0:18:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}你爸爸討厭媽媽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.61,0:18:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}不要媽媽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.36,0:18:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.40,0:18:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}一定是從一開始就不喜歡我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.91,0:18:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}一定是從一開始就不想要我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.29,0:18:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}所以跟媽媽一起死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.60,0:18:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}爸爸已經不要我們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.20,0:18:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}我很礙事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.87,0:18:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}不要我了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.56,0:18:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}跟～我～一～起～死～吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.92,0:18:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}不要！我不是媽媽的洋娃娃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.31,0:18:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}我要自己思考，自己活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.15,0:18:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}那時候，媽媽吊在天花板上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.50,0:18:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}臉上看起來非常愉快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.92,0:18:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}可是，我非常討厭那個表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.35,0:18:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}討厭死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.04,0:18:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}討厭自己的消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.40,0:18:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}討厭男孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.22,0:19:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}討厭爸爸、媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.46,0:19:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}討厭所有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.14,0:19:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}沒有人願意保護我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.08,0:19:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}都不願意待在我身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.93,0:19:10.43,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【她期待的是什麼？】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.42,0:19:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}所以我要一個人活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.79,0:19:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}可是我討厭這樣，很痛苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.80,0:19:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}討厭孤獨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.42,0:19:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}討厭孤獨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.42,0:19:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,550)\fs34}討厭孤獨——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.40,0:19:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}不要不理我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.11,0:19:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}不要拋棄我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.56,0:19:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}不要殺我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.82,0:19:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.36,0:19:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}你父親推動的人類補完計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.63,0:19:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}這就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.49,0:19:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}這好像是其中一部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.34,0:19:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}我們也不知道真實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.76,0:19:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}只不過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.90,0:19:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}自己此刻感受到的正是事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.80,0:19:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}心中所感受到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.76,0:19:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}然後成為記憶的東西就會轉變成你的真實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.49,0:20:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}隨時間而變化的真實也是存在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.42,0:20:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}這就是事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.95,0:20:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}一切的結果嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.61,0:20:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}這就是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.49,0:20:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}事實有很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.96,0:20:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}這是其中之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.90,0:20:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}這是你期望看到的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.59,0:20:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}我期望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.22,0:20:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.22,0:20:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}破滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.45,0:20:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}沒有人得救的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.43,0:20:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.54,0:20:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}只是沒有人願意救…我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.15,0:20:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}沒有人可以救你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.04,0:20:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}這，正是你所期望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.76,0:20:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}破滅、死亡、回歸虛無
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.11,0:20:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}這是你自己期望看到的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.33,0:20:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}這就是現實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.25,0:20:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}現實是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.09,0:20:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}就是你的世界啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.04,0:20:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}跟時間、空間、他人共同存在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.74,0:20:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}你自己的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.74,0:20:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}怎麼接受怎麼認定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.54,0:20:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}都是由你自己決定的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.50,0:20:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}現在被賜予給你的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.74,0:20:51.87,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【那就是現實】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.51,0:20:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}你那無藥可救的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.40,0:20:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}是個一切早有定數的世界吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.28,0:20:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.26,0:21:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}這是你決定的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.58,0:21:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}你的心所決定的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.01,0:21:06.13,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【那就是現實】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.52,0:21:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}想要活下去的意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.09,0:21:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}想要求死的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.00,0:21:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}都是你自己期望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.24,0:21:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}你是說這個黑暗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.64,0:21:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}這個不完整的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.18,0:21:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}全都是我所期望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.44,0:21:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.58,0:21:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}你希望看到一個封閉的、自己一個人舒服的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.02,0:21:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}為了保護自己脆弱的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.67,0:21:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}為了保護自己的快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.45,0:21:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}其結果無非就是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.67,0:21:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}在封閉的空間裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.32,0:21:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}你一個人的世界裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.90,0:21:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}人無法活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.68,0:21:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}可是你卻希望世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.36,0:21:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}這個包圍著自己的世界能封閉起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.44,0:21:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}你那顆希望排除不稱心的事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.08,0:21:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}創造更孤立的世界的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.85,0:21:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}導致了這個平靜於心的小世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.65,0:21:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}這個形式，也是結局之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.05,0:21:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}這是你自己所引導的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.20,0:21:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}這個世界的終結
